        <p data-role="text">While mixed mar&#xAD;tial arts ti&#xAD;tle con&#xAD;tenders like Tif&#xAD;fany Teo are still rare, their feats are com&#xAD;mend&#xAD;able con&#xAD;sid&#xAD;er&#xAD;ing the short time the sport has taken root in Sin&#xAD;ga&#xAD;pore.</p>
    </div>

